   55   M01      MG12 1105DN008         0710  1415  M104045

   DRs:

   Id #     Project  Dss  Reference  Status          Cause
   =========================================================================
   C105457  M01      43   010/1733   Entered         Software/DCC2

   lost RRP interface, with the same symptoms that
   DCC6/RRP6 has been experiencing of late. Waited until range cal
   completed successfully. Started low level intervention to restore
   communication. Software restart (shell in and dcc_start), removed
   DCC2 from link followed by placing back in link. Tried hard reset
   at RRP. Finally tip'd in at DMT and did shutdown of DCC.
   
   
   


   Id #     Project  Dss  Reference  Status          Cause
   =========================================================================
   M104045  M01      55   010/0853   Entered         Hardware/FEG

   
   LATE ENTRY. Unexpected coolant flow drop caused interlock open and
   uplink lost for six minutes from 0853-0859z. Wait for alarm to
   clear, then reinitiate uplink MAQ.
   
   CMD     LOST           8
   DOP2    LOST           8
   RNG     LOST          46
   


   Id #     Project  Dss  Reference  Status          Cause
   =========================================================================
   G107400  M01      26   010/1637   Entere          Hardware/X20KW

   
   TXR vacuum over current interlock present. Unable to continue
   uplink activities. Command session had been completed. Continued
   in downlink only mode when applicable. Other data recoverable from
   DSS25 and DSS43.
   
   TLM     LOST           4
   DOP2    REC           19
   DOP2    DEG           14
   DOP2    LOST           4
   RNG     LOST         103
   
   





